\LoggerLevel

Defines the minimum set of levels recognized by the system, that is <i>OFF</i>, <i>FATAL</i>, <i>ERROR</i>, <i>WARN</i>, <i>INFO</i>, <i>DEBUG</i> and <i>ALL</i>.

The LoggerLevel class may be subclassed to define a larger level set.
